{"title":"和为零","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1661","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>请考虑一个由 1 到 N(N=3, 4, 5 ... 9)的数字组成的递增数列:1 2 3 ... N.<br>现在请在数列中插入“+”表示加,或者“-”表示减,抑或是“(空格)”表示空白,来将每一对数字组合在一起(请不在第一个数字前插入符号).<br>计算该表达式的结果并注意你是否得到了和为零.<br>请你写一个程序找出所有产生和为零的长度为 N 的数列.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>单独的一行表示整数 N (3 &lt;= N &lt;= 20).</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>按照 ASCII 码的顺序,输出所有在每对数字间插入&ldquo;+&rdquo;, &ldquo;-&rdquo;, 或 &ldquo; &rdquo;后能得到和为零的数列.</p>\n<p>(注意:应该保留空格)</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>7</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1+2-3+4-5-6+7<br>1+2-3-4+5+6-7<br>1-2 3+4+5+6+7<br>1-2 3-4 5+6 7<br>1-2+3+4-5+6-7<br>1-2-3-4-5+6+7</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}